            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>In marketing, a meme is a humorous image, video, or text format adapted from internet culture to promote a brand, product, or idea. Brands use memes to generate organic reach and engagement without paid promotion, leveraging shareable formats that spread through social networks.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
