              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Instagram (Reels and carousels), TikTok (short-form video), and X (Twitter) are the primary meme distribution platforms. Reddit is where many meme formats originate before crossing to mainstream social media. LinkedIn is growing as a platform for B2B-specific meme content.</p></div></div>
